# Telangana

![Top to bottom: World Heritage Site Ramappa Temple; Kakatiya Kala Thoranam at Warangal Fort; Telangana Assembly; B. R. Ambedkar statue in Hyderabad; Charminar; Bhuvanagiri Fort, Nagarjuna Sagar Dam; Golconda](/Ramappa_Temple)
